On line 184 and 187 of [Mi Scale 2](https://github.com/oliexdev/openScale/blob/master/android_app/app/src/main/java/com/health/openscale/core/bluetooth/BluetoothMiScale2.java), is this a typo or the data is really used for two distinct things?

```
final boolean isDateInvalid = isBitSet(ctrlByte1, 6);
final boolean isCattyUnit = isBitSet(ctrlByte1, 6);
```

Thanks :D

