Add absolute body fat and muscle on DataEntry, Overview, Table and Chart so that the users can also monitor whether they lose or gain fat or muscle when their weight changes.

@oliexdev I understand from this issue #4 that you wouldn't like to clutter the app with too much measurements. I generally agree but I still think that absolute values of muscles and fat would be of value for the user (at least for me).

I made them configurable so the user can disable this feature. For discoverability I initially turned them on.

